      "span_text": "Results from preliminary study on Cosmos caudatus Kunth extracted with different concentration of ethanol and water (100:0, 80:20, 60:40, 50:50 and 40:60) showed that Cosmos caudatus Kunth extracted with 100% ethanol (EECCL) exhibited best pancreatic lipase, antioxidant activity and highest phenolic and flavonoid content  ."
